#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pet_groomer.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong>Appointments</strong> – Let customers book grooming services online with predefined services and\n"
"                availability."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການນັດໝາຍ</strong> – ໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຈອງບໍລິການເສີມສວຍທາງອອນລາຍ ດ້ວຍການກຳນົດບໍລິການ ແລ"
"ະ\n"
"                ເວລາທີ່ວ່າງໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ."

#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:pet_groomer.appointment_type_grooming_service
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong>Bath &amp; Dry</strong> – wash with pet-safe shampoos, conditioners,"
" blow-dry."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ອາບນ້ຳ &amp; ເປົ່າແຫ້ງ</strong> – ອາບນ້ຳດ້ວຍແຊມພູ ແລະ ຄີມນວດທີ່ປອດໄພສຳລັບສັດ, ພ້ອມ"
"ເປົ່າຂົນໃຫ້ແຫ້ງ."

#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:pet_groomer.appointment_type_grooming_service
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong>Brushing &amp; De-shedding</strong> – remove loose fur, undercoat, "
"reduce shedding."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຫວີຂົນ &amp; ກຳຈັດຂົນລົ່ນ</strong> – ເອົາຂົນທີ່ຫຼຸດລອກ ແລະ ຂົນຊັ້ນໃນອອກ, ຊ່ວຍຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການ"
"ລົ່ນຂອງຂົນ."

#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pet_groomer.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid "<strong>Calendar 🗓️</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ປະຕິທິນ 🗓️</strong>"

#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pet_groomer.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong>Calendar</strong> – Visualize and manage grooming sessions, staff schedules, and availability in one\n"
"                place."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ປະຕິທິນ</strong> – ສະແດງ ແລະ ຈັດການຮອບບໍລິການ, ຕາຕະລາງພະນັກງານ ແລະ ເວລາທີ່ວ່າງ"
"ໄດ້ໃນ\n"
"                ບ່ອນດຽວ."

#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:pet_groomer.appointment_type_animal_wellness
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong>Coat Conditioning Treatments</strong> – special shampoos, oils, or "
"masks."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການບຳລຸງເສັ້ນຂົນ</strong> – ໃຊ້ແຊມພູສູດພິເສດ, ນ້ຳມັນບຳລຸງ ຫຼື ມາກຂົນ."

#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:pet_groomer.appointment_type_animal_wellness
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong>Creative Grooming</strong> – coat dyeing, fur sculpting, accessories"
" (bows, bandanas)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການເສີມສວຍແບບສ້າງສັນ</strong> – ການຍ້ອມສີຂົນ, ຕັດແຕ່ງຊົງຂົນ, ເພີ່ມເຄື່ອງປະດັບ (ໂບ, ຜ້"
"າພັນຄໍ)."

#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:pet_groomer.appointment_type_animal_wellness
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<strong>De-matting</strong> – untangling severe knots in long-haired breeds."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ກຳຈັດຂົນພັນກັນ</strong> – ແກ້ຂົນທີ່ກອດກັນເປັນກ້ອນສຳລັບສັດພັນຂົນຍາວ."

#. module: pet_groomer
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pet_groomer.welcome_article_body
#, fuzzy
